   - [articles](http://ruby.about.com/lr/restful_authentication/384407/3/)

3. Jon Yurek, gem 
   [paperclip](http://github.com/thoughtbot/paperclip/),

   - [strona domowa gemu](http://www.thoughtbot.com/projects/paperclip)

